    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/eb1b6621e7c733c244ff4fbefbc67dc8.poster.avif?t=1742747481\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/eb1b6621e7c733c244ff4fbefbc67dc8.webm?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/eb1b6621e7c733c244ff4fbefbc67dc8.mp4?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少女在荒凉的世界睁开眼，听到来自屏幕前的“你”的声音。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以指挥她的行动，替她解开谜团、躲避危险，寻找离开这里的方法。当然，你也可以不这么做，甚至更坏心点，刻意让她死亡……开玩笑的，你肯定不会那样做吧？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不再扮演任何角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你就是你，在屏幕前指引艾莉丝的你。 <br>你可以真诚、你可以欺瞒；你可以协助、你可以破坏。 <br>但别忘了，你无法躲在其他身分后面。 <br>她会记得──记得你做的一切。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/3fc6f578ff795e1baf4c75f17c50234b.poster.avif?t=1742747481\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/3fc6f578ff795e1baf4c75f17c50234b.webm?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/3fc6f578ff795e1baf4c75f17c50234b.mp4?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索荒芜的世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >远方的高塔、无人的废墟，以及不知名的怪物。 <br>带领她继续往前，见证留下的残骸与他们的故事。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/cc00e27d929f22913474056a5bb5a528.poster.avif?t=1742747481\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/cc00e27d929f22913474056a5bb5a528.webm?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/cc00e27d929f22913474056a5bb5a528.mp4?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合道具与解谜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景获得的道具，能触发不同互动效果。 <br>组合道具挖掘更多可能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/9ebc6ae45f4cf8c4982aefe5d432cd00.poster.avif?t=1742747481\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/9ebc6ae45f4cf8c4982aefe5d432cd00.webm?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/9ebc6ae45f4cf8c4982aefe5d432cd00.mp4?t=1742747481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259820/extras/190734fac014b8f11bc6dfb0c1323905.avif?t=1742747481\" width=620 height=418 /></span></p>",
